text: Alexander Betten Hansen (born 1 November 1996) is a Norwegian football defender who plays for Mjøndalen IF. He played youth, B and C team football for Odd until the summer of 2015, when he moved on to Fram Larvik. He joined Mjøndalen in 2018, helped them win promotion to 2019 Eliteserien and made his Eliteserien debut in June 2019. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian footballers Category:Mjøndalen IF players Category:Norwegian First Division players Category:Eliteserien players Category:Association football defenders
